data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT!!! This immaculate well maintained home has everything you need to enjoy lake living in comfort! A 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath, eat-in kitchen with lovely large bay windows, separate dining area, high ceiling living room with fireplace and electric window shades, inside laundry room, tons of closet space/storage, a 3 sided screened in porch that can serve as another living room area, attached garage, a newer AC with an advantage plan (transferable), Well is 3 years old, Metal roof, a whole house Generac generator to ensure you can fully enjoy those rainy days on the lake! As an added bonus, this house has any man's dream shop! Space for all the tools he has and wants to have, an arm saw and other tools may convey if desired- inquire with listing agent. Sellers spared no expense to ensure this home has it all. Situated on Coronado lake, this home has 3.68 acres, majestic wild-life, great fishing, all in a peaceful setting for you to enjoy. All of this, just 15 minutes from Lady Lake/The Villages and Belleview, 4 minutes from Lake Weir.     Make your appointment to see this one today.
